Title: mail: make the long output of HTML mails more readable
Level: 1
Component: notifications
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Edition: cre
State: unknown
Version: 1.6.0b3
Date: 1562072699

The mail script now replaces '\n' in the long output by '&lt;br&gt;'
so that every line of the long output is now a separate line in the
HTML output as well.
